name: Madroñal
address: Plaza de la Emperatriz, 12, 28044 Madrid, Spain
review: Always great service here. Amazing for cañas and tapas, not so much for ordering in but I've not BC tried the menu yet.  Always busy but attentive service.....

name: Botafumeiro
address: Calle de la Parra, 42, 28025 Madrid, Spain
review: Look no further if you're in the Oporto area and in search for some value sized tapas and fresh seafood. The folks here at Botafumeiro will take care of you.... Excellent Service for our party of 7. We tried the best plates and were pleased with the quality. Delicious Cava sparkling and Albariño white wine....

name: La Quietud Tiyoweh
review:
Very yummy overall! We ordered the special, and a pitcher of lemonade. We could see the waitress hand squeeze the lemons, with mint and water, and so it was.... Terrific service, waitress spoke great English and was willing to offer suggestions.  Location was excellent with inside and street seating.
Food was.... Delicious!! I highly recommend.  Such a delightful space. And, the people were lovely!.

name: Casa Lucio
address: Plaza de la Emperatriz, 13, 28019 Madrid, Spain
review: A little away from the tourist traps of the plaza this place has fantastic food.  Prices are not cheap but you get a very high Michelin level meal..
